Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.64,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}So, are the days no sweeter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:59.48,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}I got 'em on their knees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:02.49,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Rotten to the core deeper, I couldn't hate them more
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:06.72,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}I have reawakened for revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:10.62,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}All these petty rules won't stop me now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.47,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}They chew up and spit you out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.28,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Statue will leave a body count
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:16.19,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}But I'm getting stronger every day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.99,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Life is now a game I like to play
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:19.93,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}I give back the light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:21.93,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}It gimme what I please
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:23.74,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Like the Ring of Gyges
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.94,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Cuz I'm back in this game
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.80,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:31.50,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Dya know I could be the star of the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:33.42,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Cuz I'm back in this game
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:35.26,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}We can survive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:39.03,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}And nothing will crush this hunter's pride
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.08,0:02:42.58,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}The pain inside us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:43.17,op en,tag,0,0,18,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Trillion and one G on a bungee all stan
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.75,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Should never go away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:46.50,op en,tag,0,0,18,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Swelling my crescendo see a window
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.62,0:02:49.75,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Despite the violence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:50.63,op en,tag,0,0,18,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}My miraculous story began provin' it to plato that I won't go shallow
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.42,0:02:53.90,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Shall never run away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.88,op en,tag,0,0,18,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Gonna be a player super slayer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:55.94,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Cuz I'm back in this game
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.77,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:01.43,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Dya know I could be the star of the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.35,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Cuz I'm back in this game
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.03,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}We can survive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:08.86,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}And nothing will crush this hunter's pride
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.06,0:03:12.27,op en,,0,0,2,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}The pain inside us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:13.65,op en,,0,0,18,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Gonna trap it uh uh gonna trap it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.65,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Should never go away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:17.28,op en,,0,0,18,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Gonna stack it up yeah I'm a tap it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.64,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}没错 正如
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:59.48,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}已巅峰不再的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:02.49,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}腐烂更进一步深入核心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:06.72,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}然而我为复仇再次觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:10.62,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}无论这规则如何荒诞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.47,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}他们将你吞噬 再吐出你的残渣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.28,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}雕像将会记录伤亡人数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:16.19,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}满怀初生之犊的渴望与焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.99,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}曾经那副模样已被黑暗浸透
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:19.93,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}我回馈璀璨的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:21.93,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}一切会令我心满意足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:23.74,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}戴上裘格斯的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.94,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}因为我重新回到这场游戏里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.80,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}所以让我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:31.50,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}超越既定的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:33.42,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}因为我重新回到这场游戏里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:35.26,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}我们可以幸存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:39.03,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}于挣扎之中不断打磨猎人的骄傲
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.08,0:02:42.58,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}我们内心深处的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:43.17,op zh,tag,0,0,20,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}令人承受着难以衡量的压力 就像蹦极一样 令人享受其中
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.75,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}永远不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:46.50,op zh,tag,0,0,20,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}羽翼渐丰 我的实力慢慢增强 一丝机会浮现眼前
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.62,0:02:49.75,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}杂念中的沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:50.63,op zh,tag,0,0,20,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}我的传奇故事拉开序幕 亲自向柏拉图证明 我不会变得浅薄无知
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.42,0:02:53.90,op zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}无法拼接的导火索
